data.description: This lovely home features an open concept floor plan. To the right of the entry, you'll find a large secondary bedroom and secondary bath. Moving past the stairs, the home opens to a great room and spacious kitchen. The kitchen offers a large island with pendant lighting above, recessed lighting, granite countertops, and Whirlpool® appliances. Upstairs, an open loft is perfect for family movie nights. Two secondary bedrooms, a secondary bath, and the laundry can be found adjacent to the loft. The master suite covers the entire back of the home and features an oversized walk-in closet. The spacious master bath boasts a separate garden tub, a shower with tile surround, and a dual-sink vanity. Please call for more information.
